stork.module.ftp

Class FTPChannel.DataChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • stork.module.ftp.FTPChannel
      • stork.module.ftp.FTPChannel.Lock
        • stork.module.ftp.FTPChannel.DataChannel
  • Enclosing class:
    FTPChannel

    public class FTPChannel.DataChannel
extends FTPChannel.Lock
    Asynchronous FTP data channel abstraction. Subclasses must override receive(Slice) to handle incoming data. This channel extends Lock, but handles its own unlocking.
